name: MACHINA 02 - Prison of Thoughts
description:
From the "MACHINA Limited Series"

We all think, as a result of which we create thoughts and ideas that form dreams. Dreams are known to be a sensation of wants or do. For each that you have ever had and decided to not act upon, where do they go? 
How hard would it be to navigate through the prison of dreams, a self-built labyrinth haunted by the abandoned cries of dreams unrealized? 

Prison of Dreams is an actual dream by the artist brought to the digital canvas and stored on the blockchain.
